snippet.title: Galactic Warrior
snippet.description:
Dowload on Google play: https://goo.gl/23vBkH

Help the galactic warrior to conquer all the arenas of the universe.
Hard action game and incredibly fun, for all those who loves challenges.

Galactic Warrior is an fast paced action game, where you must defeat waves of enemies to obtain gold, armors, and... ¡Reach the glory!

FEATURES:
- 10 skills (pasives and actives) that you could buy and upgrade.
- Get armor parts to comlpete it and upgrade it.
- Upgrade your sword getting experience.
- Defeat Final Bosses in each Arena.
- Beutiful Pixel Art.
- Fun to play.
